  <p>Activities in this phase include:</p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
   <li>define the problem (with the team) MVP / what to test / needs to be met</li>
 <li>define the scope</li>
 <li>define the gaps</li>
 <li>challenge assumptions</li>
 <li>define tasks to complete</li>
 <li>create design histories (TBC if IxD task or team task)</li>
 <li>review user stories reflect identified user needs</li>
 <li>stakeholder management (as appropriate)</li>
        </ul>       
