  <p>Activities in this phase include:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
   <li>collaborate and feed into User Research so we learn how users behave, their needs and pain points and identify any gaps</li>
 <li>evaluate and evolve / iterate prototypes / journeys based on UR or design review</li>
 <li>Collaborative Design Reviews</li>
 <li>collaborate on dev build</li>
 <li>support accessibility testing</li>
 <li>documentation (design histories)</li>
 <li>share learnings</li>
 <li>stakeholder management (as appropriate)</li>
  </ul>
